		h2#colleges.mt-5 College System
		hr
		p Oxford has a college system (similar to CUHK). The accommodation and food differ depending on which college you are in. However, we will have our lectures and practicals in the Computer Science Department regardless which college you are in.

		p Instead of a centralized campus like most universities in Hong Kong, the colleges and departments are scattered around the city, which felt a strange thing to me at first.

		h3#univ University College
		p My college is called University College (Univ), one of the oldest colleges in Oxford. Here are some pictures of what my college looks like (with captions). It is moderately sized and it looks nice and old. :)

